cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CY, cs.SI 

This paper deals with privacy-preserving machine learning, specifically weighted federated learning, within the context of multi-party computation (MPC) and cryptography. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves machine learning, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The use of MPC suggests cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as another possible category. The paper also deals with privacy and cryptography, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
